Here’s how you can make that badge color shift automatically based on the audit date inside your JSON file:

```html
<a href="a11y.json" aria-label="Accessibility audit record">
  <svg id="a11yBadge" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="130" height="24">
    <rect id="badgeRect" width="130" height="24" rx="4" fill="#004d4d"/>
    <text x="8" y="16" fill="#ffffff" font-size="12"
          font-family="Segoe UI, Arial, sans-serif">
      ♿ Accessibility ✔︎
    </text>
  </svg>
